nodes.text: Cult of M'dweshuu Sisar Run murders

In 22 BBY, the Nikto death Cult of M'dweshuu launched a string of homicidal murders along the Sisar Run hyperlane of the Periphery region. During the attacks, the cult killed at least twenty–seven beings, and the Jedi Council began investigating the murders. The HoloNet News later reported on the murders.
